# Slim the `railway up` upload context (Dockerfile.belt + Dockerfile.erpc builds).
# Mirrors .dockerignore, plus .claude — the latter contains broken symlinks to an
# uninstalled construct pack (.claude/skills/* -> ../constructs/packs/archivist/...)
# that crash `railway up`'s file indexer ("No such file or directory"). The builds
# need none of these: belt = src/ + config.mibera.yaml + schema.graphql + package.json
# + pnpm-lock.yaml + Dockerfile.belt; eRPC = erpc.yaml + Dockerfile.erpc. node_modules
# is reinstalled in-image (pnpm install --frozen-lockfile).
